window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Betrayed by allies. Beset by new foes. Earth faces its darkest hour since the Xaros invasion. </p> <p>The Toth come to the solar system with a fleet of warships, and they demand the only tool that can rekindle the human race. It falls on Marine Lieutenant Hale to negotiate a pact that will save the human race at the cost of its soul - or start a war with a race of alien predators. </p>"; 
